lon and remove them. I need to be in Tai Po at twenty to ten tomorrow morning but I'm not sure if I could face getting up early enough to catch the bus that will get me to Tai Po at twenty past nine. Should I take a taxi instead? I would appreciate any help you could offer. I used to live in Tokyo. I still remember my maid taking me to trick or treat as a kid but after we had moved to where I now live we didn't go trick or treating anymore as it isn't popular in here."}]}